THIRD-PARTY CRATE DEPENDENCIES

  • pitch-core — MIT OR Apache-2.0 (this workspace)
  • ndarray, ort, thiserror — MIT OR Apache-2.0

The `ort` crate by default downloads pre-built ONNX Runtime binaries
(~50 MB). See <https://crates.io/crates/ort> for build-time options
that link a system-provided ONNX Runtime instead.

Run `cargo about generate` against this crate to produce a complete
attribution file for redistributable binaries.
